END, [dto.Product].[Name], [dto.Product].[CategoryId], [dto.Product].[Price] AS [Price0], [dto.Product].[PromotionPrice], [dto.Product].[OriginalPrice], [dto.Product].[Description], [dto.Product].[Content], [dto.Product].[HomeFlag], CAST(COALESCE([dto.Product].[HotFlag], 0) AS bit) AS [HotFlag], [dto.Product].[ViewCount], [dto.Product].[Image], [dto.Product].[Tags], [dto.Product].[Unit], [dto.Product].[Status], [dto.Product].[SeoPageTitle], [dto.Product].[SeoAlias], [dto.Product].[SeoKeywords], [dto.Product].[SeoDescription], [dto.Product].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [dto.Product].[DateModified], CASE
    WHEN [dto.Product].[CategoryId] IS NOT NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [dto.Product.ProductCategory].[Id] AS [Id0], [dto.Product.ProductCategory].[Name] AS [Name0], [dto.Product.ProductCategory].[Description] AS [Description0], [dto.Product.ProductCategory].[ParentId], [dto.Product.ProductCategory].[HomeOrder], CAST(COALESCE([dto.Product.ProductCategory].[HomeFlag], 0) AS bit) AS [HomeFlag0], [dto.Product.ProductCategory].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [dto.Product.ProductCategory].[DateModified] AS [DateModified0], [dto.Product.ProductCategory].[SortOrder], [dto.Product.ProductCategory].[Status] AS [Status0], [dto.Product.ProductCategory].[SeoPageTitle] AS [SeoPageTitle0], [dto.Product.ProductCategory].[SeoAlias] AS [SeoAlias0], [dto.Product.ProductCategory].[SeoKeywords] AS [SeoKeywords0], [dto.Product.ProductCategory].[SeoDescription] AS [SeoDescription0]
FROM [BillDetails] AS [x.BillDetails]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [dto.Product] ON [x.BillDetails].[ProductId] = [dto.Product].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [dto.Product.ProductCategory] ON [dto.Product].[CategoryId] = [dto.Product.ProductCategory].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [x0].[CreatedDate], [x0].[Id]
    FROM [Bills] AS [x0]
    ORDER BY [x0].[CreatedDate] DESC, [x0].[Id]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t] ON [x.BillDetails].[BillId] = [t].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[CreatedDate] DESC, [t].[Id], [x.BillDetails].[Id], [dto.Product.ProductCategory].[Id]" (0723d8ff)
